data.description: Welcome to your charming colonial-style brick home nestled in the serene neighborhood of Whispering Trails. Boasting three bedrooms, the primary bedroom and bathroom host a spa like oasis that has a heated jet tub. This residence is a perfect blend of classic design and modern comfort. As you step inside, the freshly painted walls greet you with a calming neutral palette, creating an inviting atmosphere throughout. Venture down to the finished basement, where another fireplace beckons, providing a perfect setting for entertainment or a quiet retreat. This additional space adds versatility to your home, accommodating various needs and desires as there is a full bathroom as well. Sunlight enthusiasts will adore the sunroom, a delightful haven for basking in the natural glow that floods through its windows. Large back deck perfect for gathering or just relaxing outside. Situated on a generous 3.08-acre. 2022 Roof, & HVACA 2023 New hot water heater.
